snippet.title: Dragon's Dogma 2 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Set forth on your grand adventure, Arisen. Follow thy heart to seek the truth. Pre-order Dragon's Dogma 2 now! Coming to PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S and Steam on March 22, 2024.
